title: Jimi Hendrix 3 (1968-1970)
description:
This is the 3rd of 3 DVD-As of my world class Jimi Hendrix (1966-1970) compilation. Essentially they are remastered static pictured music videos al la TubeYou. Because Jimi's non sister is a greedy bitch, you cannot download most of his music that way. I had to use Wondershare Slideshow maker to create 80% of the content but rest assured it is worth your bandwidth and time if you love the man's music. I have only been listening to Jimi since the very early 1970s but believe that is long enough to know what bee wot Jimi-wise. Nice background pictures have been used for the extensive menu's etc. Let me know what you think of this? 

"Plays on normal DVD players. No need for expensive equipment etc"
